        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 04:08:47 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 04:08:47 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="STEVE KARNOWSKI, Associated Press, PHL 17">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/21/tim-walz-is-still-introducing-himself-to-voters-here-are-things-to-know-about-harris-vp-pick.webp" alt="Tim Walz is still introducing himself to voters. Here are things to know about Harris' VP pick"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tim Walz is still introducing himself to voters. Here are things to know about Harris' VP pick</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      MINNEAPOLIS (AP) — Kamala Harris' running mate, Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz, will face a national audience that's still getting to know him when he headlines the Democratic National Convention in Chicago on Wednesday night.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/21/tim-walz-is-still-introducing-himself-to-voters-here-are-things-to-know-about-harris-vp-pick/"  >(STEVE KARNOWSKI, Associated Press, PHL 17)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:00:08 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:00:08 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Urja Sinha, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/20/obama-2004-dnc-speech-legacy.webp" alt="Looking back on the legacy of Obama's 2004 keynote DNC address"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Looking back on the legacy of Obama's 2004 keynote DNC address</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The self-declared “skinny kid with a funny name” entered the national spotlight after his speech at the 2004 DNC.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/20/obama-2004-dnc-speech-legacy/"  >(Urja Sinha, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 19:42:20 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 19:42:20 +0000">
