           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">This Latino immigrant CEO is working to serve his community &#8212; here's how</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Latino Connection is bridging the gap between health care, education, government services and the Latino community.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/20/this-latino-immigrant-ceo-is-working-to-serve-his-community-heres-how-2/"  >(Taylor Tosheff, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
