           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Panama deports 29 Colombians on first US-funded flight</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      PANAMA CITY (AP) — Panama deported 29 Colombians on Tuesday on a flight that the government said was the first paid for by the United States under an agreement the two countries signed in July.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/21/panama-deports-29-colombians-on-first-us-funded-flight/"  >(Associated Press, KREX 5)</a>
    </p>
