    <p itemprop="text">
      Mosab Hassan Yousef discussed the troubling signs he sees in America of an administration that has too much trust in the good faith of Hamas to negotiate a meaningful deal.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/18/son-hamas-founder-insists-no-thing-israel-hamas-ceasefire-ayatollah-gone/"  >(Fox News)</a>
