        <div class="row"><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 22:30:15 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 22:30:15 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/08/17/volcano-erupts-after-powerful-earthquake-in-russias-far-east-and-scientists-warn-of-a-stronger-one.webp" alt="Volcano erupts after powerful earthquake in Russia's Far East and scientists warn of a stronger one"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Volcano erupts after powerful earthquake in Russia's Far East and scientists warn of a stronger one</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      One of Russia’s most active volcanoes has erupted, spewing plumes of ash 3 miles into the sky over the far eastern Kamchatka Peninsula and briefly triggering a “code red” warning for aircraft.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/17/volcano-erupts-after-powerful-earthquake-in-russias-far-east-and-scientists-warn-of-a-stronger-one/"  >(Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
