    <h3 itemprop="headline">Workplace of the future: Three must-haves of a modern printer</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      By Chris White, Director of Global Product Portfolio for Lexmark International
The modern workplace thrives on sleek tablets, cloud storage and ways to go paperless. Yet, amid this digital hum, a familiar presence persists – the office printer.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/20/workplace-of-the-future-three-must-haves-of-a-modern-printer/"  >(CIO)</a>
    </p>
