    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump, Vance counter DNC message by shifting focus to crime</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Republicans are zeroing in on crime even while violent crime rates are declining in major cities.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/20/trump-vance-counter-dnc-message-focus-crime/"  >(Tom Dempsey, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 14:00:00 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 14:00:00 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Estelle Timar-Wilcox, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/19/longtime-st-paul-mayor-george-latimer-dies-at-89.webp" alt="Longtime St. Paul mayor George Latimer dies at 89"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Longtime St. Paul mayor George Latimer dies at 89</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      George Latimer served as mayor of St. Paul from 1976 until 1990, the longest run of anyone in the city’s history. He oversaw St. Paul’s downtown boom, a growth in development amid a changing city. Latimer died on Sunday at age 89 at his residence in St. Paul.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/19/longtime-st-paul-mayor-george-latimer-dies-at-89/"  >(Estelle Timar-Wilcox, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset></main>
